YVV Aditya
Ph no.  +91 9176480365
Email id  venkatadit2@gmail.com

PS: It's a team event. Maximum of 2 members can be there in a team.
PPS: Participants are expected to bring their laptops and mouse for the
sessions and the event.

Regards,


Vinay Mittal

